@startuml
title Activity Diagram: UC-09 Monitor Delivery Progress

|Owner|
start
:Navigate to 'Delivery Tracking' dashboard;

split
  :Select a specific rider on map;
  |System|
  :Display detailed order info popup;
split again
  |System|
  :Continuously poll GPS coordinates;
  if (Rider GPS is off?) then ([Yes])
    :Display last known location;
    :Show GPS Warning Icon;
  else ([No])
    :Overlay live rider locations on map;
    :Update estimated delivery times;
  endif
end split
stop
@enduml
